It was like a blank slate with a stage, and I saw people filling these with white tile—the cheap sticky tile you put down in grocery stores that you polish with wax.

00:30:44.240 --> 00:30:57.239
I could see the white tiles and metal folding chairs all throughout this building, full of Cuban people.

00:30:57.240 --> 00:31:07.385
They were on the stage, having worship with guitars, pianos, and drums, giving God praise.

00:31:07.386 --> 00:31:12.279
There were probably five or six thousand people in this building.

00:31:12.280 --> 00:31:22.513
And I saw them in Cuba being raised up like megachurches all throughout Cuba with major congregations, and they were all celebrating Jesus.

00:31:22.514 --> 00:31:31.039
Some of them had flags and were twirling them, celebrating Jesus and their freedom.

00:31:31.040 --> 00:31:54.615
They were celebrating what God had done; some of them were crying and weeping before the Lord because they were no longer bound by a dictator.

00:31:54.616 --> 00:32:09.719
I could see it again: they were worshiping Jesus. Things changed quickly; financial blessing.

00:32:09.720 --> 00:32:19.479
Now they said, "Do you agree with smoking cigars, Brandon?"I didn't tell you I agree—I don't agree with smoking anything—but I tell you what I saw.

00:32:19.480 --> 00:32:42.427
I saw cigar factories all over the place, and they were being shipped to America, Europe, Africa, and China in boatloads because there was so much production of this stuff on a greater, higher level.

00:32:42.428 --> 00:32:52.697
Now, I don't know if Europe already has all that; I don't know if Africa already has it. I'm telling you where it was and what I saw, Braden.

00:32:52.698 --> 00:33:07.279
I saw arrows coming out to Canada and these places, coming out of factories; it looked like Indiana Jones, how it goes from place to place when he travels in the movie.

00:33:07.280 --> 00:33:16.041
That's the way it was coming out of these factories in Cuba, and it became a big business.

00:33:16.042 --> 00:33:21.633
Cigars—I thought it was interesting, like global trade with cigars.

00:33:21.634 --> 00:33:27.319
Now, do I think smoking cigars is good? No, I'm telling you what I saw.

00:33:27.320 --> 00:33:41.688
So, I thought that was interesting. I think that's it, right?

00:33:41.689 --> 00:33:48.982
Yeah. He saw burning. I don't know what that was. What is it? Like, what do you call it?

00:33:48.983 --> 00:33:53.528
I'm sorry... cremation. Yeah, I told him; I said incinerates him.

00:33:53.529 --> 00:33:58.039
Okay, cremation. Yeah, and he saw gold coins and all that. Yeah, he saw Taiwan.

00:33:58.040 --> 00:34:02.639
I saw all that. And then the Lord told me we should pray for Taiwan.

00:34:02.640 --> 00:34:16.158
I saw Taiwan and a plan that was coming about from China to do just like what we did to Venezuela in the middle of the night.

00:34:16.159 --> 00:34:29.799
And the Lord said they're devising a plan, Xi Jinping right now, to take Taiwan, and in this, it will be just like Venezuela.

00:34:29.800 --> 00:34:39.678
But as I was praying, I saw Australia and other nations that were fussy about it.

00:34:39.679 --> 00:34:50.607
It was not like, "We'll send aid, we'll send this, we'll send whatever."It didn't look like a lot of rebuttal.

00:34:50.608 --> 00:34:58.251
What I want to say is I was praying for the de-escalation of World War III in Asia.

00:34:58.252 --> 00:35:13.405
The one who was the most upset about it was South Korea. The most upset after that was Japan and those other Asian nations.

00:35:13.406 --> 00:35:24.519
China took it in the vision. It looked like China took it effortlessly, but as I saw it, I'm still praying that it will not happen.

00:35:24.520 --> 00:35:35.637
I'm still praying this will not happen, but I saw it again. It looked like it was just something that was boom, boom, boom.

00:35:35.638 --> 00:35:53.119
This is why I pray against attacks on Hawaii, because I kept seeing Hawaii, Honolulu being hit to make it where our military people can't go over and help out of Hawaii.

00:35:53.120 --> 00:36:06.223
Praying over these things, there's still a lot there. There's a lot of things, and in this, I was bouncing around, but most of the vision last night was praying over Cuba in the darkness in the still of the night.

00:36:06.224 --> 00:36:21.159
A new chapter will come out of darkness. A new chapter is about to come forth, a new beginning. A new era of time is coming for the Cuban people.

00:36:21.160 --> 00:36:29.489
The same with the Venezuelans, the same with, I believe in the days ahead, Mexico and Colombia.

00:36:29.490 --> 00:36:40.719
There's going to be shaking in these nations. But right now, I believe with all my heart, we could see this tomorrow.

00:36:40.720 --> 00:36:46.959
We could see this Sunday, Monday, whatever. I'm just telling you, I just feel in my heart it's about to happen.

00:36:46.960 --> 00:36:52.519
Could it be a year from now? It could. I don't believe it will be.

00:36:52.520 --> 00:36:59.285
It's everything the Lord has showed us about the darkness. He said it will happen in darkness.

00:36:59.286 --> 00:37:04.622
And if you go back and watch my old videos, the Lord warned us countless times it will happen in darkness.

00:37:04.623 --> 00:37:14.863
They will shut down the grid in Cuba. I have video after video after video talking about the grid will shut down.

00:37:14.864 --> 00:37:24.005
America will use cyber warfare against Cuba and turn off their lights. The Lord told us this.

00:37:24.006 --> 00:37:31.003
How many times did the Lord tell us that they would turn off their lights in the middle of the night and there would be an invasion?

00:37:31.004 --> 00:37:42.369
There'll be these things coming. We have to pray for them, our troops, to liberate the people of Cuba in the days ahead.

00:37:42.370 --> 00:37:54.274
I appreciate you all helping me pray over that. The other part was praying over this Iranian conflict, praying over our military bases.

00:37:54.275 --> 00:38:07.239
I saw again a surprise attack coming to Israel in the middle of the night that will be worse than October 7th.

00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:31.679
The Lord said they're devising a plan with Hezbollah to retaliate with this surprise warfare, with chemical biological warfare in the middle of the night against Israel. It will not be with rockets.

00:38:31.680 --> 00:38:58.519
I saw some kind of thing they were using like a crop duster, and I saw a biological attack coming out of the Damascus area against the Israeli people, and the Lord said this will be worse than October the 7th.

00:38:58.520 --> 00:39:02.710
And I said, "Pray for Israel. Pray for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:39:02.711 --> 00:39:08.159
Pray for the innocent bystanders and the civilians that are there.

00:39:08.160 --> 00:39:16.719
It would not be just missiles."I saw megaton missiles that were bigger being brought to them.

00:39:16.720 --> 00:39:26.538
China gives them new weapons in the days ahead. I saw this, though I don't know how they would get them.

00:39:26.539 --> 00:39:36.119
I mean, we usually think you'd blow them out of the sky if they were bringing them on planes, but I saw secret weapons coming somehow.

00:39:36.120 --> 00:39:49.759
I don't know. As the Strait of Hormuz is going to be barred, I saw it being shut down. I saw boats on fire.

00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:59.676
I saw a major conflict happening in this Strait, and Pakistan gets involved in the days ahead.

00:39:59.677 --> 00:40:09.319
It got more and more as this happened. Remember what the Lord said: it happens for a window.

00:40:09.320 --> 00:40:17.039
A window doesn't last very long. A window is small. A door is big. The Lord didn't say a door; he said a window.

00:40:17.040 --> 00:40:22.221
This conflict in this area will be a window and it will be short-lived.

00:40:22.222 --> 00:40:33.759
And in doing so, he said Trump will say, "Drill, baby, drill."And he will open up new pipelines that have been closed.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:44.318
He will open up new things for strategic oil reserves throughout America to bring the petrodollar to where it needs to be.

00:40:44.319 --> 00:40:53.679
And I saw our economy pumping oil with fracking and all kinds of things. We're going to become the oil capital of the world.

00:40:53.680 --> 00:41:03.439
Lifting some of these bans on "Hey, you can't drill here, you can't drill here"—by the law of the land, we're saying we can.

00:41:03.440 --> 00:41:13.074
So when I told you all that, what did Gavin say today? "You can't touch the oil."And there was an oil line.

00:41:13.075 --> 00:41:19.312
And he said, "We lost how many barrels of oil out of it?"We're opening up again, and there's oil just like the Lord said.

00:41:19.313 --> 00:41:25.648
President Trump's going to open up pipelines. There is one in California Gavin's freaking out about: "You're not opening it.

00:41:25.649 --> 00:41:30.318
It leaked oil and we condemned it in 2015."And now we're opening it up again.

00:41:30.319 --> 00:41:41.019
He says, "Right. Do you have the article? It goes with what the Lord showed me."So we see those things happening.

00:41:41.020 --> 00:41:45.568
So will we see "drill, baby, drill"? I believe with all my heart, and I believe you're going to see it in Gaza.

00:41:45.569 --> 00:41:56.894
I believe you're going to see it in all kinds of places. And we're going to see Israel and America be buddies with oil, gas, and money.

00:41:56.895 --> 00:42:03.719
Watch what happens. For the people in Oklahoma, maybe we'll have another oil boom.

00:42:03.720 --> 00:42:07.839
It makes our economy good because that's what our main thing is here in Oklahoma.

00:42:07.840 --> 00:42:17.385
The 1980s in Tulsa was an oil-booming city. Do you have it? Is that right?

00:42:17.386 --> 00:42:23.599
Play it. I want to show them, and then I want to start praying.

00:42:23.600 --> 00:42:26.973
So, what the Lord said is what I'm trying to tell you. All glory to Jesus.

00:42:26.974 --> 00:42:33.479
Energy Secretary Chris Wright ordered the reopening of an offshore oil operation and pipeline in California.

00:42:33.480 --> 00:42:39.552
The Santa Ynez unit operates off the coast of Santa Barbara. However, it had a major shakeup in 2015.

00:42:39.553 --> 00:42:45.239
Its pipeline ruptured and spilled nearly 3,000 barrels of oil into the Pacific Ocean.

00:42:45.240 --> 00:42:50.472
Wright's order came hours after President Trump invoked the Defense Production Act on Friday.

00:42:50.473 --> 00:42:58.107
In response, California Governor Gavin Newsom said it's illegal because multiple court orders have forbidden the restarting of this pipeline.

00:42:58.108 --> 00:43:04.436
The Energy Department says the order will address supply disruption risks and reduce reliance on foreign oil.

00:43:04.437 --> 00:43:12.839
According to the Energy Information Administration, the US has been a net exporter of oil since 2019.

00:43:12.840 --> 00:43:15.803
Energy Secretary Chris Wright ordered. Isn't that amazing?

00:43:15.804 --> 00:43:23.679
It's just like the Lord said. Jesus is wonderful. He tells us what's coming in the news before it happens.

00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:32.805
It's pretty neat. So, you know how many people say, 'Brandon, you work for Mossad'? How dumb is that? I've had more people say that lately.

00:43:32.806 --> 00:43:42.301
'We know you're in Israeli special intelligence, Brandon.'And I'm like, y'all are smoking some bad weed.

00:43:42.302 --> 00:43:48.823
I mean, seriously, you're smoking some real bad weed. I don't work for Israeli intelligence.

00:43:48.824 --> 00:43:53.232
I'm not a part of American intelligence. I pray for our president.

00:43:53.233 --> 00:43:58.768
So, get off your bad weed. Don't smoke that stuff. It's making you sick.

00:43:58.769 --> 00:44:07.155
It's bad for you. Don't smoke that stuff, or crack or whatever else you're smoking.

00:44:07.156 --> 00:44:13.159
It's bad for you. All right, let's pray. You want to pray with me?

00:44:13.160 --> 00:44:17.183
I was so excited how many people got born again last night. Wasn't that wonderful?

00:44:17.184 --> 00:44:21.388
We had seventy-some people. Seventy! Isn't that wonderful?

00:44:21.389 --> 00:44:28.483
I just go, Jesus is so amazing that he would use a little YouTube channel. Here we are.

00:44:28.484 --> 00:44:33.719
People come and they give their hearts to Jesus Christ because they're curious about what's coming in the future.

00:44:33.720 --> 00:44:41.559
'If I be lifted up, he'll draw all men in.'I believe with all my heart we're seeing just the beginning.

00:44:41.560 --> 00:44:55.486
We're seeing just a little bit of spring forth of growth when the Lord said, 'I'll make you known throughout the whole world, Brandon. Like a Billy Graham, you'll bring them in.

00:44:55.487 --> 00:45:04.079
Brandon, tell them I'm coming.'And I told him, 'I'll do it.'And you always know when you're doing right because you get persecuted the hardest when you're bringing in souls.

00:45:04.080 --> 00:45:15.879
And as I told everybody—and I say this, I shouldn't have said some things I've said about saying that if you don't lead people to Jesus that you're a false prophet.

00:45:15.880 --> 00:45:27.868
I know there are some people that have really good hearts, but I don't ever really give an excuse to ministries not leading altar calls and giving people an opportunity to accept Jesus Christ.

00:45:27.869 --> 00:45:32.879
I even called them false prophets, and I shouldn't have said that that day.

00:45:32.880 --> 00:45:42.846
I was really bold about it and even said, 'Ministers and pastors, you're not real pastors if you're not leading people to Jesus.'And I come against the church, and the Lord always corrects me.

00:45:42.847 --> 00:45:49.559
He says, 'You need to watch how you say things and walk in love, Brandon.

00:45:49.560 --> 00:46:01.719
You need to walk in love.'And I come across probably as a jerk a lot of times on certain things I say, but I truly mean in my heart you should be getting people saved.

00:46:01.720 --> 00:46:11.279
I don't know why you wouldn't. What does it hurt you to give a five-minute altar call, pastors?

00:46:11.280 --> 00:46:13.460
Well, I don't know. 'Well, I know everybody in here.'Five minutes.

00:46:13.461 --> 00:46:16.159
It just takes a couple minutes to give people an opportunity.

00:46:16.160 --> 00:46:25.039
Maybe they're not right with the Lord and you believe you're just expecting them to be right, and you don't ever give them an opportunity to change.

00:46:25.040 --> 00:46:39.439
You don't give them an opportunity to make a choice. There are so many mega churches where maybe, you know, one thing about the church where we used to go to, he gave an altar call every single week.

00:46:39.440 --> 00:46:45.927
And I'd go back and count all the people who got saved, and we would get truckloads of people saved.

00:46:45.928 --> 00:46:55.793
Truckloads every week. Sometimes we'd get over 150 to 600 in a big revival service or whatever. They would come in and we'd bring them in from downtown.

00:46:55.794 --> 00:47:06.282
So, they had a women's ministry that went to the strip clubs and they would talk to the strippers and to the people there, and they would try to get the strippers saved.

00:47:06.283 --> 00:47:09.102
I believe they called it Daughters of Eve or something like that.

00:47:09.103 --> 00:47:17.039
I don't remember, but they were always trying to reach the lost, always trying to get people out of the pit of hell.

00:47:17.040 --> 00:47:27.919
And I respect that about a church. I'll support you until the cows come home if you're getting people saved.

00:47:27.920 --> 00:47:36.679
Give people an opportunity to make a choice. I remember what it was like to be lost.

00:47:36.680 --> 00:47:42.319
I remember being on the verge. If I would have died, I would have gone to hell.

00:47:42.320 --> 00:47:44.735
Living in the world, you think, 'Oh, you know, I'm going to live in sin.

00:47:44.736 --> 00:47:51.479
You're going to do all this stuff. I'm just going to make it.'No, you have to be separate.

00:47:51.480 --> 00:47:56.033
Now, I'm going to tell you, I know grace covers a multitude of sins. I get it.

00:47:56.034 --> 00:48:08.439
But you don't deliberately bathe in sin and say, 'I'm going to live this way and have a good time.'Be holy as I am holy, and you try.

00:48:08.440 --> 00:48:16.679
God forgive me, but I believe a real ministry in these last days should be a soul-winning ministry.

00:48:16.680 --> 00:48:31.119
I challenge every person who's watching here: if you have a ministry, if you have a platform to give people an opportunity to accept Jesus Christ as Lord and personal savior, you're going to be held accountable for it.

00:48:31.120 --> 00:48:41.278
I truly believe that you're going to stand before the Lord, and He's going to look at you and say, 'Why did you never give My people a time?

00:48:41.279 --> 00:48:53.039
Why did you never give an opportunity? Why did you do that?''Well, you know what? It wasn't popular. I was embarrassed.

00:48:53.040 --> 00:49:04.039
I was ashamed.'If you're ashamed to speak His name, He won't speak your name before the Father.

00:49:04.040 --> 00:49:13.999
I truly believe it's time for us to become radical and get ready for His coming.

00:49:14.000 --> 00:49:28.759
It's time. We have to wake up. We're running out of time. But yet, there are so many people that act like it's just life as normal.

00:49:28.760 --> 00:49:32.959
They don't even really act like there's anything different.

00:49:32.960 --> 00:49:37.839
All around them, they keep doing the same thing, expecting different results.

00:49:37.840 --> 00:49:41.639
But they don't even try to get people saved. They don't care.

00:49:41.640 --> 00:49:55.199
Well, you know, if we had a guest come—I guess we had one person that came to our service that was new—but evangelism is the major way.

00:49:55.200 --> 00:50:02.079
Evangelism is the only way. I believe you get the evangelist coming; that's why there's a five-fold ministries.

00:50:02.080 --> 00:50:10.439
The evangelist brings the newcomers in, and the pastor keeps them. You know, you have to disciple these people.

00:50:10.440 --> 00:50:17.569
And I'm telling you, they're coming in by the big freightliner loads.

00:50:17.570 --> 00:50:23.831
It's not going to be these little bitty ones, like throwing a pole out and reeling one in.

00:50:23.832 --> 00:50:36.599
I'm talking massive shrimping boats full of people with big old nets. They're coming. What will you do? Will you help Him?

00:50:36.600 --> 00:50:40.359
The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few, ladies and gentlemen.

00:50:40.360 --> 00:50:48.239
He's the Lord of the harvest, and I just want to challenge you all to really wake up.

00:50:48.240 --> 00:51:04.266
And so if I come across critical to YouTubers or to prophetic channels or whatever and say, 'If you're not leading people to Jesus, you're a false prophet,'I say it out of frustration and I apologize to people when I say it.

00:51:04.267 --> 00:51:13.239
I shouldn't come across so rude. It doesn't make you a false prophet for not leading people to Jesus; it just makes you lazy.

00:51:13.240 --> 00:51:21.491
It's time to get radical and serious about the Lord. But I want to pray tonight.

00:51:21.492 --> 00:51:25.319
Let's pray for the lost. Let's pray for whatever He has for us to pray for.

00:51:25.320 --> 00:51:29.431
I am grateful that nothing happened today on St. Patrick's Day. We had all the parades.

00:51:29.432 --> 00:51:32.919
Everything went off without a hitch, and I don't see that anybody got hurt.

00:51:32.920 --> 00:51:41.118
So, I'm so thankful for that. We didn't have any terrorist attacks today. There weren't any lone-wolf shooters.

00:51:41.119 --> 00:51:46.359
How many times have we come out of this, and we're victorious every time, right?

00:51:46.360 --> 00:52:02.919
We believe that we will always cover our nation in prayer as praying, believing believers—not begging believers, but believing believers who believe that God is who He says He is and that Psalm 91 is ours.

00:52:02.920 --> 00:52:09.407
No hexes or vexes will come nigh any of us. Do you understand that?

00:52:09.408 --> 00:52:18.239
When they send the hexes and the vexes, they fall to our feet, but the devils they sent go back on them.

00:52:18.240 --> 00:52:26.399
Every single one of them. The people who believe in witchcraft the most—you cannot curse whom God has blessed.

00:52:26.400 --> 00:52:32.359
A thousand shall fall at my side and ten thousand at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me.

00:52:32.360 --> 00:52:41.479
So all the hexes and the vexes, they fall at my feet. And the demons that you thought you controlled turn back on you.

00:52:41.480 --> 00:52:50.559
They turn back on you. And I pray for you. I pray for you because you touch not God's anointed and you do no prophets any harm.

00:52:50.560 --> 00:52:56.199
I truly believe with all my heart He provides protection over His people.

00:52:56.200 --> 00:53:04.839
He said He would give His angels charge over us, and they bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:53:04.840 --> 00:53:16.199
So the hexes and the vexes, the satanic wizardry, the witchcraft—all the things that try to come against you—and no, it does not bear fruit in me because of the blood of Jesus.

00:53:16.200 --> 00:53:21.112
We make much of the blood. We make much of this covenant. We make much of the blood.

00:53:21.113 --> 00:53:29.679
We anoint ourselves with oil, and it makes much of us—the blood that never loses its power.

00:53:29.680 --> 00:53:35.679
We pray for you to get saved. We pray for you to turn from your wicked ways.

00:53:35.680 --> 00:53:45.839
The devil has deceived you. You believe he'll reward you in his kingdom. You believe he'll give you prosperity.

00:53:45.840 --> 00:53:58.319
You believe if you sell your soul to him and drink chicken blood or cat blood or whatever you're doing with the blood of the innocent, it's going to give you more power.

00:53:58.320 --> 00:54:02.405
It's going to give you a coven, and you're going to get to do all these things.

00:54:02.406 --> 00:54:15.439
But the bottom line is, the moment you die, you're going to spend eternity in hell, and he's going to laugh at you.

00:54:15.440 --> 00:54:26.383
He's going to laugh at you because you were so deceived. The very spells you cast with hexes and vexes and the things you do—the devils that you sent out come back on you.

00:54:26.384 --> 00:54:30.114
So I don't understand that automatically doesn't show love.

00:54:30.115 --> 00:54:40.039
God is love, and he loves you, and he wants you to turn from your wicked ways. He wants you to repent of your sins.

00:54:40.040 --> 00:55:02.279
"Seek first the kingdom, and all these things will be added unto you."The very devil that you think you can control will soon drag your soul to hell. You don't control no devil. They're playing you.

00:55:02.280 --> 00:55:12.599
And you think every single time that you do these things against Christians, and you try so hard to destroy churches and all this stuff, it gives you a power trip.

00:55:12.600 --> 00:55:18.839
But the very bottom line is the Lord shows me. He said, "Brandon, I love every single one of them.

00:55:18.840 --> 00:55:32.239
I died for every single one of them."All those that are practicing occultic witchcraft, voodoo, and sorcery—all these demonic things—he said, "I died for every single one of them.

00:55:32.240 --> 00:55:45.399
I love every single one of them. But they're in rebellion towards me."Unless a man is born again, he will not enter into the kingdom of God.

00:55:45.400 --> 00:55:54.119
And the devil is never going to overthrow God. The one that created the devil that fell laughs at the devil.

00:55:54.120 --> 00:56:08.642
He laughs at his plans. He laughs. But he's lied so much to you because it doesn't take character to be a devil.

00:56:08.643 --> 00:56:20.879
All of a sudden, when you surrendered to him and you gave him your soul and all these things happened, he gave you a lot of power really quick because he wants you to kill, steal, and destroy with it.

00:56:20.880 --> 00:56:28.399
But God, it takes you to be refined to lay down your life before him as a living sacrifice.

00:56:28.400 --> 00:56:38.479
"Jesus, I need you. I need a savior."But peace that passes all understanding belongs to the believer.

00:56:38.480 --> 00:56:50.159
The torment that you have every night when you go to bed with the demonic spirits that bother you and give you nightmares and the things that try to wrap around your mind—you don't have to live with that.

00:56:50.160 --> 00:57:01.067
Jesus loves you. He died for you. And I just pray for every single one of you that come against me, and I say, "I pray for you.

00:57:01.068 --> 00:57:12.679
I pray for God to bless you,"that you would know him as Lord and personal savior.

00:57:12.680 --> 00:57:24.319
There is a day coming when it will be too late for you. There will be a day when you'll take your last breath.

00:57:24.320 --> 00:57:30.763
